{
  "texts": [
    "These questions guide the scope and objectives of the systematic review.",
    "After establishing the research questions, we create search queries based on them and select relevant databases to search for relevant literature.",
    "These search queries are individually applied to each chosen database, ensuring comprehensive coverage of the relevant studies.",
    "The retrieved papers then undergo a manual analysis to assess their relevance based on our inclusion and exclusion criteria.",
    "In an iterative process, we refine the search queries and repeat the search until no significant changes in the results are observed."
  ]
}